The '''modest tiger parrot''' ('''''Psittacella modesta''''') is a species of [[parrot]] in the family [[Psittaculidae]]. It is found in the [[Arfak Mountains]] and [[New Guinea Highlands]]. Its natural [[habitat]] is [[subtropical]] or [[tropical]] moist [[montane forest]]s.

